data.description: **Price Improvement!**Attention Veterans, this home has an Assumable loan being offered at 2.25%** Welcome to your dream home in Azle! This captivating property offers 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and a spacious open-concept living area that is perfect for family gatherings and entertaining guests. You will love the modern kitchen with a gas cooktop and tankless water heater, as well as the elegant master suite with a walk-in closet and dual sinks. The home features high-quality finishes and fixtures throughout, and has been meticulously maintained by the original owners. The oversized backyard is a paradise for outdoor lovers, with plenty of room for a pool, a playground, or a garden. You can also enjoy the scenic views of Eagle Mountain Lake, which is just minutes away from your doorstep. This home is practically new and move-in ready, so don’t miss this opportunity to own a piece of paradise in Azle! Schedule your showing today!
